# Immutable binary artefacts — tracked by their companion .md source pages, not directly.
# Keeps the repo lean; images are only ever moved, never edited.
# PDFs ARE tracked (backup completeness): small ones in plain git, >100 MB via Git LFS
# (see .gitattributes). Do not re-add *.pdf here.
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.zip
.env
.git-note
.obsidian/
.claude/
.trash/
external-datasets/
new-queue/
my-notes/
run-overnight.logscratchpad/
